293 template <typename Derived>
294 void ChompTrajectory::getJointVelocities(size_t traj_point, Eigen::MatrixBase<Derived>& velocities)
295 {
296  velocities.setZero();
297  double inv_time = 1.0 / discretization_;
298 
299  for (int k = -DIFF_RULE_LENGTH / 2; k <= DIFF_RULE_LENGTH / 2; k++)
300  {
301  velocities += (inv_time * DIFF_RULES[0][k + DIFF_RULE_LENGTH / 2]) * trajectory_.row(traj_point + k).transpose();
302  }
303 }
304 
305 inline double ChompTrajectory::getDuration() const
306 {
307  return duration_;
308 }
